value.0: A mysterious door, set in a strange building in the wall.

A large crack mars the surface of this mirror. You can just barely make out some sort of doorway through a swirling mist when you stare long enough - perhaps a castle entrance. When you reach out to touch the surface, your hand bangs against the hard glass. 

You wonder what might have happened if not for the large crack...

When you peer into the mirror, rather than a reflection, you can make out some other location through a swirling mist. 

When you reach out to touch it, your hand passes into the mirror. Perhaps you can walk through to the destination you see...

Welcome!

You are now entering the Mirror Maze.

Beware...for many have entered here, and become lost forever. Be also aware, that you will not be alone within the maze. Only the worthy may pass through to the Electric Castle, whose gates lie at the end of this trial. 

Those unworthy who try, face grave peril in the attempt.

When you peer into the mirror, rather than a reflection, you see only a swirling mist, with a key floating in the midde. You reach toward it, but only succeed in banging your hand against the glass.

Around the frame are seven glowing stones; one blue, cyan, green, orange, red, white and yellow.

You feel as though you've seen those colours once before.
